						<div class="postbody">So which mapper would tokumaru and Drag recommend cloning instead? Consider that this product is intended for developers, and developers will want to use a debugging emulator, so it'd be best to use a mapper that's already well supported in FCEUX and Nintendulator.
<br />
<br />One slight problem with using a cycle counter is the authentic PAL NES, whose CPU runs at Fpx/3.2 instead of Fpx/3.</div>

					
